article_title: New Mexico ranks 2nd worst in U.S. for jobless rate
article_text:
Taos, NM (87571)

Today

Sunny early then partly cloudy and windy this afternoon. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. High around 65F. Winds SW at 20 to 30 mph..

Tonight

Partly cloudy skies this evening will become overcast overnight. A stray shower or thunderstorm is possible. Low 36F. Winds SSW at 10 to 20 mph.

article_metadata.author: Bruce Krasnow | The New Mexico

og.description: Only West Virginia, where unemployment stands at 6.9 percent, is higher than New Mexico, and there are just seven states with rates higher than 6 percent.
